\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cvv1665702762433.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cvv1665702762433.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cvv1665702762433.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cvv1665702762433\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Alternative Name </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property defines a descriptive name for a palette. This name is displayed in the\n      Resource Browser instead of the object name. It can contain up to 256 Unicode characters. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__section_w671ab1b5b1_w672ab1b5_w673ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__table_d10844e1_d10845e1_d10846e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Physical Name: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> UALT_NAME </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Expected Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> String of up to 256 characters. Supports\n                        Unicode. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Mandatory?: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None. If not defined, the literal object name\n                        is shown. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__section_oz5_zrh_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d690132e103\">Usage</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__p_d96998e1_d96999e1_d97000e1\">This property is only available if\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Development Purpose</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">P (Palette)</code> or\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">T (Template)</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__section_chw_gsh_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d690132e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__p_d97004e1_d97005e1_d97006e1\">Palettes and their contents are made available in the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Templates</span> tab of the Resource Browser.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__p_d97007e1_d97008e1_d97009e1\">Uniface object names are restricted in length and type\n            of characters, so you can use this property to provide a better and more readable name\n            for the object than the Uniface object name. It should preferably be unique but this is\n            not enforced.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__section_ytc_nsh_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d690132e136\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__ul_twf_4sh_nwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cvv1665702762433__li_d39416e1_d39417e1_d39418e1\">Palettes </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/osd1692183897129.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Templates and Palettes</a><p>Templates are development objects that are copied during development to create new objects. Uniface provides an extensive set of default templates, but you can also create your own.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612475\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612475\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Alternative Name Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Alternative Name This property defines a descriptive name for a palette. This name is displayed in the Resource Browser instead of the object name. It can contain up to 256 Unicode characters. Physical Name: UALT_NAME Expected Value: String of up to 256 characters. Supports Unicode. Mandatory?: No Default Value: None. If not defined, the literal object name is shown. Usage This property is only available if Development Purpose is P (Palette) or T (Template) . Description Palettes and their contents are made available in the Templates tab of the Resource Browser. Uniface object names are restricted in length and type of characters, so you can use this property to provide a better and more readable name for the object than the Uniface object name. It should preferably be unique but this is not enforced. Applies To Palettes Related Links Templates and Palettes Templates are development objects that are copied during development to create new objects. Uniface provides an extensive set of default templates, but you can also create your own. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}